<p>When trying to understand the various ways Real Madrid played during the LaLiga season, it’s important to look at goals such as; Goals For (GF) and Goals against (GA) utilizing these two different stats. Gives us a chance to understand the strength the team has when tackling with goals.</p>
<p>For instance, during the 2024-2025 season, Real Madrid has scored about 53 goals with the highest goals against opponent being 80 proving, that during that season Real Madrid had a strong offense, rather than defense. Studying a chart about goals isn’t only about the goals that they were able to get, but rather a result of how much effort and training was put in the offensive side.</p>
