<p>To better understand the difference of ranking, I ranked the team as a whole to see how the ranking has changed and what actually happened that led to these results. I compared 2023-2024 and 2025-2026, which gave a result of how the performance of the team has changed.</p>
<p>For instance, during the 23-24 season Real Madrid scored 95 points making them first ranked, with wins about 85 points, making Barcelona second ranked at the time.</p>
<p>Looking at the ranking of a team, tells a story, not only about the coaching, but rather the results that speak louder than words. Looking at these charts have proven that changes in coaches, will have an impact on the team performance. It is clear that a coach can be good at training an offensive side than coaching a defensive side.</p>



